The Weapons table shows all weapons (Melee, Ranged and Magic) that are currently in Old School RuneScape, showing their attack and defence bonuses.

Note: Two-handed weapons, such as claws and godswords, are not listed here. Instead, they are found here.

Also note that because weapons have different speeds you can not directly compare their attributes. To compare weapons you should ideally use a DPS calculator, but a reasonable alternative is to use Calculator:Armoury and toggle Normalize. Normalize scales strength-like attributes with the weapon's speed. At least for melee weapons this can be used as a proxy for damage output. With ranged weapons, the ammo will have a big effect on damage so keep that in mind. Likewise for magic weapons, the spell is the most significant factor for the damage.
